/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oracle headquarter building in Bucharest. Logo of the Oracle company on a office building.\" data-id=\"1261350454\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4448px\" height=\"3271px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cristi Croitoru</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>I Totally Underestimated Oracle's Growth</h2> <p>I underestimated the ability of Oracle Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a></span>) to continue its remarkable performance over the past six to seven months, even though I upgraded ORCL in my previous update. <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4695678-oracle-turbulence-avoided-might-still-be-hard-to-defy-gravity-rating-upgrade\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4695678-oracle-turbulence-avoided-might-still-be-hard-to-defy-gravity-rating-upgrade\" target=\"_blank\">In my Oracle article</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1261350454/image_1261350454.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743512-oracle-stock-post-earnings-decline-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 19:30:45"}, {"id": "4743607", "title": "Berkshire Hathaway: P/B Ratio Still Matters", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Why It Matters. your future target searching, a marker, pen, three colored pencils and a notebook for writing\" data-id=\"1269717570\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"880px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alena Butor/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>BRK stock\u2019s chart of the day</h2> <p>My last analysis on Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRK.A\" title=\"Berkshire Hathaway Inc.\">BRK.A</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRK.B\" title=\"Berkshire Hathaway Inc.\">BRK.B</a></span>) was published on Oct. 22, 2024. That <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4728417-berkshire-hathaway-continued-equity-divestitures-signal-uncertainty\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4728417-berkshire-hathaway-continued-equity-divestitures-signal-uncertainty\" target=\"_blank\">article</a>, under the title of \"Berkshire Hathaway: Continued Equity Divestitures Signal Uncertainty,\" rated the stock as a </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1269717570/image_1269717570.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743607-berkshire-hathaway-pb-ratio-still-matters", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 19:23:20"}, {"id": "4743606", "title": "S&P 500: A Year-End Record, A Challenging 2025, And A 'Lost Decade'", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/679379743/image_679379743.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Arrows\" data-id=\"679379743\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1130px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/679379743/image_679379743.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/679379743/image_679379743.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/679379743/image_679379743.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cd